{"tid":664379,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"汶川大地震10年過去仍有人活在陰霾中","createTime":"2018-05-14T04:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T04:57:20.000Z","uid":70063,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5faee9f5da062aa623dbef9262761e8f348c7c84","tid":664379,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:53:23.000Z","msg":"汶川大地震造成6萬9千多人死亡。有志願組織負責人指，10年過去，部份災難中生還的人，仍然活在地震的陰霾之中。有痛失子女的父母會因為稍為笑一下而感到罪過，亦有父母考慮再生育，但如何對待災後的子女，成為一大考驗。另一個受影響的群體，是災後心理受創的年輕人，部份失學及流連網吧，長大後從事色情行業，成為社會問題。隨著志願機構介入，情況近年慢慢有改善。但最新調查推算災區仍然有約2百萬人，有「創傷後壓力症」，不願意接受心理支援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1007684&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1007684%26csid%3D261_341&d=BzsFvvO4moS6CNL1%2FM7kiB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=68495278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1007684&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"f562f52af6d123b06ce111809db9175416b88d82","tid":664379,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:54:07.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"a5c62ef3317f943dc62ad3f82bd9d07b405b06e1","tid":664379,"uid":163350,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:57:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}